---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions | Catalyst Digital Marketing" 
       description="Get answers to common questions about our digital marketing services, pricing, process, and more.">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-secondary-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Frequently Asked <span class="text-primary-600">Questions</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Find answers to common questions about our services, process, and how we can help grow your business.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        
        <!-- General Questions -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">General Questions</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            
            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-1">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What makes Catalyst different from other marketing agencies?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-1" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">We focus exclusively on measurable results and ROI. Unlike agencies that just create campaigns, we build comprehensive growth systems. Our team has experience at companies like Google and HubSpot, and we've helped 200+ businesses achieve an average 347% revenue increase. We're transparent with our methods, provide detailed reporting, and work as true growth partners.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What types of businesses do you work with?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-2" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">We work with businesses across various industries including SaaS, e-commerce, healthcare, professional services, and B2B companies. Our ideal clients are businesses generating $10K+ monthly revenue who are ready to scale. We focus on companies that value data-driven strategies and are committed to long-term growth.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-3">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How quickly can I expect to see results?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-3" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Timeline varies by service: Paid advertising typically shows results within 2-4 weeks, SEO takes 3-6 months for significant impact, and social media growth is usually visible within 4-8 weeks. We provide monthly reports and track progress continuously. Most clients see meaningful improvements within the first 90 days.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pricing & Contracts -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Pricing & Contracts</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            
            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-4">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What's included in your pricing?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-4" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our pricing includes strategy development, campaign management, content creation, optimization, reporting, and dedicated account management. Ad spend is separate and goes directly to platforms like Google and Facebook. There are no hidden fees or setup costs. Everything is transparent and outlined in your service agreement.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-5">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you require long-term contracts?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-5" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">We work on a month-to-month basis with 30 days notice for termination. However, we recommend at least 3-6 months to see optimal results from our strategies. Some services like SEO and content marketing require longer timeframes to be effective, which we'll discuss during your consultation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-6">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-6" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely! You can upgrade your plan at any time and changes take effect immediately. Downgrades take effect at the start of your next billing cycle. We'll work with you to ensure a smooth transition and adjust strategies accordingly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services & Process -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Services & Process</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            
            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-7">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What's your onboarding process like?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-7" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our onboarding takes 1-2 weeks and includes: (1) Strategy session to understand your goals, (2) Account setup and access configuration, (3) Competitive analysis and market research, (4) Custom strategy development, (5) Campaign launch and initial optimization. You'll have a dedicated account manager throughout the process.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-8">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How do you measure and report results?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-8" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">We provide comprehensive monthly reports covering all key metrics: traffic, leads, conversions, ROI, and revenue attribution. You'll have access to real-time dashboards and receive detailed analysis with actionable insights. We focus on metrics that directly impact your business goals, not just vanity metrics.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-9">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you work with our existing tools and platforms?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-9" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Yes! We integrate with most popular platforms including HubSpot, Salesforce, Shopify, WordPress, Google Analytics, and more. We'll audit your current tech stack and recommend optimizations or additions only when necessary for better results.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Getting Started -->
        <div class="animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Getting Started</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            
            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-10">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What happens during the free strategy call?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-10" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">During our 30-minute call, we'll discuss your business goals, current marketing challenges, and growth opportunities. We'll provide initial recommendations and explain how our services can help. There's no sales pressure – our goal is to understand if we're a good fit for each other.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-11">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What information should I prepare for our consultation?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-11" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">Come prepared with: your business goals and challenges, current marketing activities and budgets, target audience information, competitor insights, and access to analytics if available. Don't worry if you don't have everything – we'll help you identify what's needed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
              <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-600 rounded-lg" data-target="faq-12">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How soon can we start working together?</h3>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
              </button>
              <div id="faq-12" class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-600">We can typically start within 1-2 weeks of signing the agreement. This allows time for proper onboarding, account setup, and strategy development. For urgent projects, we may be able to expedite the process depending on our current capacity.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-secondary-600">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll text-white">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Still Have Questions?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-white/90">
          Book a free strategy call and get personalized answers to your specific questions.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
          Book Free Strategy Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script>
  // FAQ accordion functionality
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const faqQuestions = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question');
    
    faqQuestions.forEach(question => {
      question.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const targetId = question.getAttribute('data-target');
        const answer = document.getElementById(targetId);
        const icon = question.querySelector('svg');
        
        // Close all other answers
        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-answer').forEach(otherAnswer => {
          if (otherAnswer.id !== targetId) {
            otherAnswer.classList.add('hidden');
            const otherIcon = otherAnswer.previousElementSibling.querySelector('svg');
            otherIcon.classList.remove('rotate-180');
          }
        });
        
        // Toggle current answer
        answer.classList.toggle('hidden');
        icon.classList.toggle('rotate-180');
      });
    });
  });
</script>